{
  "stem": "15732.4",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And from Czechoslovakia, you in turn will be taken by somebody else that will take you to Austria.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And from Austria, we'll take you to Munich.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And in Munich, there is the Jewish Brigade there who will look after you.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Basically it wasn't the Jewish Brigade there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was again somebody from-- but it doesn't matter.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Again, I was the-- the powerhouse that started to pummel my parents.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The little bit that they bought from Tschernowitz, little bit, we had to leave now, because again with the rucksack, we have to go through Europe.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And not only that, but my father had severe angina, so that to schlep a person who is sick is not-- But I must confess that I just didn't have the-- the wisdom to think what I do to my father that I can't really pay with his life.",
      "word_count": 49
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But I knew only that I want to live and I don't want to live in Poland and I don't want to live in Europe and I would like to go to Palestine.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And after pummeling-- after severe pummeling from their daughter, they-- my parents agreed to go with the rucksack through Europe.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I'll tell you how we get there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We went on the train, again a organized group.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We went on a train.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The train stopped middle of the night at some border.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "When we came to the border, the guide-- I call that young man the guide.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were not allowed to know even their names.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There had to be such a colossal anonymity, we were not allowed to know the name or to call them even.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He took us-- he organized the group.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He counted as many as he has and said, follow me.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we followed.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
